result.name: sen-ryo

reviews.text: Just so good. This is a standard 'fast food' joint for my family and I.  We love sushi and Sen Ryo have everything we like (and trust me, in Asia you get some weird things!) and the cost is very reasonable for what you get. Happy with their service and the restaurants are all clean and tidy.

The best sushi I ever eat ! Obviously, it follows with a high price tag. I will recommend to try at least once in your life because it's worth it. I really enjoyed every bites of every dishes! Probably the best in the world ❤️
On standard and stable at quality, don't demand for suprise.

Good quality sushi at a fair price, only disappointment was a lot of the menu items were out of stock including uni.  Seating is comfortable and staff are attentive and friendly.  Overall a good experience and recommended place.  The wait is usually not too long as this location is slightly off the beaten path.
Great place for sushi 😁 enjoy alot

result.name: Fashion Walk

reviews.text: This is a trendy shopping area located conveniently in Causeway Bay. There's a collection of fancy boutiques & clothing stores from various designer labels. The products are pretty high-end, meaning they could be pricier than the average store. Nonetheless, everything feels so glamorous and fashionable. This shopping area should appeal to a young demographic for sure.
Shop staff is friendly introducing the brand and they have nice product designs at KLASSE14 shop.
Small but nicely set up mall.  With Logon & Starbuck on 1st floor, I can spend a whole afternoon here. Clean washrooms on ground level. Convenient for visitors.
It has very good brands that you can't find commonly
Easy to get to & meet up with friends for a light bite & drinks. Really quaint & a nice variety to choose from. Not overly crowded too. A nice mix of eclectic groups of people and visitors.

result.name: 千両

reviews.text: 好吃😋
沒來用餐約三個月，很多客服不同了，服務也差了。客服經過餐枱數次也不主動收起已吃完了食物的餐碟，要出聲才收取。以前的客服很用心，經常留意食客的情況，會主動添茶收碟。
中上價位日本魚生壽司食堂！品質有保証！食物種類也多！雖然經常要排隊，但還是很多客人的！當然比不上日本的築地或豐洲，但在香港也算是不錯的選擇！

地方較細。
